Category:Imperial Navy officers of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: This Imperial officer served aboard the Super Star Destroyer Executor during the Galactic Civil War. Three months after the Battle of Hoth, this officer reported to Darth Vader that a new shipment of Viper probe droids had arrived aboard the Executor and that a new group of bounty hunters waited onboard to join in the hunt for Luke Skywalker.

This character appears in the Infinities comic Star Wars Infinities: The Empire Strikes Back, and thus is non-canon. The story represents an alternative scenario for Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back in the event that Luke Skywalker dies from his wampa encounter on Hoth.
